content:
@MichaelAntonF @PrincessPlo no, what makes money is three things:
1. goods/services priced in this thing (unit of account)
2. exchanging goods/services for this thing (medium of exchange)
3. goods/services being stable against this thing (store of value)
For now Bitcoin doesn't achieve any of the 3.
